        <content type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;github-repository&quot;&gt;Github Repository&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;emptyfridge0900&#x2F;HereCheck&quot;&gt;Click here&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;project&quot;&gt;Project&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is part of capstone project called HereCheck. HereCheck is a fully automate attendance recording system. Taking the advantage of updating face recognition technology, our solution helps taking students&#x2F;employees attendance with ease. HereCheck consist of three programs that includes Server, Face Recognition, and Web-App UI. This program is Web-App UI for instructors&#x2F;employers to view and manage all the records. &lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;features&quot;&gt;Features&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Display attendence records in real time &lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Display login page, faculty page and admin page&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select program&#x2F;courses and attendance sheet page &lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create programs, create courses, create user accounts, update and delete them.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
